      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/cou/cou1-cpb/applicability-constraint",
      "type": "ApplicabilityConstraint",
      "name": "CPB hemolysis CFD applicability domain",
      "description": "Model is applicable to Newtonian blood analog at hematocrit 35–45%, pump speeds 2000–3500 RPM, and flow rates 3–7 L/min for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry. Model is not applicable to non-Newtonian regimes, pediatric sizing, or pump speeds outside the validated range."
    },
