      "name": "CPB operating envelope — validated bounds",
      "description": "Flow rate: 3.0–7.0 L/min; Pump speed: 2000–3500 RPM; Inlet pressure: 5–15 mmHg; Outlet pressure: 60–120 mmHg; Blood temperature: 35–37 °C; Hematocrit: 35–45%; Geometry tolerance band: ±0.15 mm on all wetted surfaces. Operating outside these bounds invalidates model predictions without additional validation."
