      },
      "rationale": "Three meshes: 4.2M, 7.8M, 14.6M cells (refinement ratio 1.31). GCI on normalized hemolysis index: 1.4% at production mesh (7.8M). Monotonic convergence confirmed. Wall y+ < 1 on all wetted surfaces. Production mesh selected as optimal cost-accuracy trade-off."
