      },
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions from FDA GCBP hemolysis protocol (ASTM F1841) documented with calibrated instrumentation (NIST-traceable). CFD boundary conditions set from measured time-averaged values. Deviation from nominal: flow rate ±0.8%, speed ±0.5%, inlet pressure ±1.1%. All within ±2% acceptance band."
