        "name": "Independent simulation reproduction by second analyst; results agree within 1%",
        "description": "A second qualified analyst must independently reproduce the simulation setup from documentation alone and obtain hemolysis index results within 1% of primary analyst results at all 5 operating points."
      },
      "rationale": "Independent reproduction performed by analyst B (FDA-cleared CFD practitioner) using only the simulation specification document SSD-2023-07. NIH results at all 5 operating points agree within 0.6% of primary analyst results. Discrepancies traced to floating-point initialization; resolved by standardizing random seed. Use error contribution quantified and negligible."
