        "description": "At least 5 independently manufactured test articles must be tested; geometric variation between units must be measured by CMM and incorporated as an input uncertainty source in the total uncertainty budget."
      },
      "rationale": "Six independently manufactured FDA GCBP test articles tested per ASTM F1841 protocol. CMM measurement of all 6 articles: maximum geometric deviation 0.09 mm from nominal, inter-unit standard deviation 0.03 mm. Inter-unit variability incorporated as geometric uncertainty input in Monte Carlo UQ. Blood samples from 3 separate porcine donations used across test articles."
